  "Cc1": {
   "media": [
     "<p>Cc1 is a very rare, almost theoretical climate that typically occurs near the boundary with another climate category. It is found on Heard Island in the coastal, mossy areas, bordering the Dc1 climate. The inside of a typical refrigerator could technically be said to have a Cc1 microclimate.</p>",
